l over how and what you think. It means being conscious and aware enough to choose what you pay attention to and to choose how you construct meaning from experience. Because if you cannot exercise this kind of choice in adult life, you will be totally hosed.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source: <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.vercel.app\/great-speeches\/this-is-water-by-david-foster-wallace\"><em>This is Water<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Look around the rooms where you spend the most time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What behavior does this space encourage? How can you set things up to make your good habits easier?<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Until next week,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Clear <br><em>Author of the #1 worldwide bestseller, <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\/\"><em>Atomic Habits<\/em><\/a><em>\u200b <\/em><br><em>Creator of the <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.vercel.app\/habit-journal\"><em>Habit Journal<\/em><\/a><em>\u200b<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200b<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>p.s. <a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.vercel.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/fair-question.png\">Fair question<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>3 IDEAS FROM ME I. &#8220;Most people optimize for the day ahead. A few people optimize for 1-2 years ahead. Almost nobody optimizes for 3-4 years ahead (or longer). The person who is willing to delay gratification longer than most reduces competition and gains a decisive advantage. Patience is power.&#8221; \u200bII. &#8220;The biggest risk to [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":40295,"menu_order":0,"template":"","acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v20.5 (Yoast SEO v20.6) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>3-2-1: The value of nature, controlling your attention, and designing your environment - James Clear<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-sn